0:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using the premium/discount between perpetual and mark prices. The funding rate is capped at ±0.75% to prevent extreme payments during high volatility. When funding is positive, long positions pay shorts; when negative, shorts pay longs. Bybit's unified margin account allows traders to use cross-collateral for funding rate strategies without separate position management."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
